## Why Longevity Herbs Survived

Traditional herbal systems rarely treated aging as something to “defeat.”

Instead, many focused on:
- maintaining resilience
- supporting recovery
- preserving movement and circulation
- reducing long-term inflammation
- nourishing the body consistently over decades

That slower philosophy is part of why these herbs survived while countless miracle remedies disappeared.

