## Simple Traditional Routine

Morning:
- green tea

Day:
- turmeric with food

Evening:
- gotu kola infusion or astragalus decoction

Seasonally:
- ginseng during periods of exhaustion or depletion

Traditional herbal systems usually emphasized small daily habits repeated over years rather than aggressive short-term “anti-aging” cures.

